WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.280 --> 01:37.552
=Episode 29=

01:45.040 --> 01:48.840
Mingxi, we have no way out now.

01:49.200 --> 01:51.840
Once the Eastern Palace rises,
everything will be fine.

01:51.840 --> 01:52.640
You wish.

01:53.200 --> 01:56.400
You think he'll make you a high official
when he becomes Emperor?

01:57.400 --> 01:59.799
You've done so many dirty deeds for him.

02:00.280 --> 02:01.799
You know it in your heart.

02:03.319 --> 02:05.000
If he wants to seem honest
and righteous,

02:05.359 --> 02:07.239
the first person he'll silence is you.

02:07.760 --> 02:09.199
He is not that kind of person.

02:09.520 --> 02:11.400
- Zuidie and I trust him.
- Don't mention her again.

02:12.439 --> 02:14.840
You've truly been bewitched
by that woman.

02:16.479 --> 02:19.199
I'm telling you, she framed Ye Li.

02:20.199 --> 02:21.840
I will definitely kill her.

02:35.560 --> 02:37.199
(Mo Jingli.)

02:40.479 --> 02:42.120
With the death of Princess Lingyun,

02:42.840 --> 02:44.159
Cangbei will surely be enraged.

02:45.039 --> 02:46.360
Peace will be hopeless.

02:47.280 --> 02:49.240
War might even break out immediately.

02:50.520 --> 02:53.439
They previously ordered Zhang Hengyuan
to kill Zhong Xingtong.

02:53.919 --> 02:55.560
That was meant to sow discord.

02:57.639 --> 02:58.759
Mo Jingli.

02:59.599 --> 03:02.280
Are you really going
to persist on the wrong path?

03:04.919 --> 03:06.560
I never meddled in their matters.

03:09.159 --> 03:10.080
Fine,

03:10.719 --> 03:13.919
you didn't before.
And never meddle then.

03:15.800 --> 03:19.159
From now on, you'll be a regular worker
at Shende Shop.

03:22.240 --> 03:23.240
Ye Li,

03:25.639 --> 03:27.280
do I still have a chance?

03:42.439 --> 03:44.280
Why not put it in the pond?

03:45.479 --> 03:48.319
Mix some river water with the pond water
and let it stay for a few days,

03:48.919 --> 03:52.120
so it can slowly get used to the water.

03:52.280 --> 03:54.319
Then it'll be better
to put it in the pond.

03:55.800 --> 03:57.240
Very thoughtful of you.

03:59.159 --> 04:01.560
From now on,
it's going to live at our home.

04:01.680 --> 04:03.199
Naturally, we must treat it well.

04:18.519 --> 04:20.040
Just like when a person leaves home,

04:23.079 --> 04:25.160
they watch the moon
to feel less homesick.

04:41.040 --> 04:42.040
You miss Lishan Mountain?

04:44.519 --> 04:45.759
If there's a chance,

04:46.920 --> 04:49.136
I'll take you back to Lishan Mountain
to see the moon.

04:49.439 --> 04:51.240
Isn't the moon the same anywhere?

04:51.759 --> 04:54.360
Is the moon above Lishan Mountain
different

04:54.680 --> 04:55.800
from the one above us?

04:56.040 --> 04:56.920
Of course.

04:58.759 --> 05:01.959
The moon above Lishan Mountain
is so big.

05:03.360 --> 05:05.519
Lying in the courtyard every night,

05:06.560 --> 05:09.199
I felt as if it was embracing me.

05:10.759 --> 05:11.959
Lying in the courtyard?

05:12.680 --> 05:14.560
Did you watch the moon every night?

05:14.839 --> 05:15.959
What about other disciples?

05:16.439 --> 05:18.759
I don't know.

05:20.240 --> 05:22.839
Every night,
I watched it rise through the branches.

05:23.759 --> 05:26.800
Sometimes, some clouds trailed the moon.

05:28.800 --> 05:31.319
And the moon there is very bright.

05:31.920 --> 05:33.120
When it snows,

05:33.959 --> 05:36.199
the moonlight and the snowlight
blend together.

05:36.879 --> 05:40.624
When walking in the snow,
you'll feel like you're in a fairyland.

05:46.040 --> 05:48.959
Alright, we'll go this winter.

05:50.079 --> 05:53.519
We can happily watch the snow
under the moonlight.

06:03.536 --> 06:06.832
(Xiangqi Pavilion)

06:12.839 --> 06:13.639
Are you hungry?

06:14.240 --> 06:15.920
A new eatery opened on the street.

06:15.920 --> 06:17.160
Their lamb dumplings are good.

06:17.279 --> 06:18.399
Want to go try some?

06:21.800 --> 06:24.800
How about noodles? Or noodle soup?

06:27.000 --> 06:29.680
You have an appetite, but I don't.

06:31.040 --> 06:33.240
Why not?
Are you full from drinking water?

06:33.319 --> 06:34.519
My stomach is full of anger.

06:37.639 --> 06:39.920
Li Feibai! Mr. Li!

06:40.279 --> 06:41.720
You're really something.

06:42.439 --> 06:43.160
Listen,

06:43.680 --> 06:46.319
yesterday at Xihua,
it was such a big show.

06:46.839 --> 06:49.399
Many people
were watching my performance.

06:50.040 --> 06:53.279
Even the Vice Minister of Revenue,
just transferred from Qinzhou, was there.

06:53.639 --> 06:55.360
When my performance was
at a crucial moment,

06:55.480 --> 06:56.272
what did you do?

06:56.272 --> 06:59.759
You suddenly carried me off
like a sack of grain!

07:05.199 --> 07:06.920
Do you know
what the consequences would be?

07:07.480 --> 07:09.879
What consequences?
Just get someone else to perform.

07:11.000 --> 07:11.800
Li Feibai!

07:13.759 --> 07:15.000
Stop yelling.

07:16.279 --> 07:19.399
Listen, you shouldn't
have learned dancing at all.

07:19.504 --> 07:23.079
With your good voice,
you should've learned singing instead.

07:29.424 --> 07:30.360
Don't be mad.

07:34.610 --> 07:36.930
Don't use this perfume anymore.
It's too strong.

07:37.451 --> 07:39.851
Mind your own business.
Who are you to me?

07:43.730 --> 07:46.011
Who am I to you? You tell me.

07:48.091 --> 07:50.810
Feibai, what you did yesterday

07:50.971 --> 07:53.451
ruined my reputation
and broke the business rules.

07:53.810 --> 07:56.170
In the future,
nobody will pay me to perform.

07:56.891 --> 07:58.571
And I won't be able to earn any money.

08:00.531 --> 08:03.050
That's easy. I'll compensate you.

08:06.091 --> 08:08.531
Compensate? You can do that this time,

08:09.290 --> 08:10.771
but can you do that for a lifetime?

08:11.250 --> 08:13.651
Alright, then I'll compensate you
for a lifetime.

08:19.971 --> 08:21.571
Anyone can talk big.

08:22.610 --> 08:25.810
Buying my freedom costs a lot of money.

08:26.971 --> 08:28.050
How much?

08:30.211 --> 08:31.571
A lot, anyway.

08:32.211 --> 08:34.530
And I'm not easy to support.

08:35.811 --> 08:37.650
You don't even have a house right now.

08:37.971 --> 08:40.730
In the future,
where will I live with you?

08:41.370 --> 08:44.091
You can't expect me
to drift around with you.

08:45.650 --> 08:48.250
Also, if you want me
to be your concubine,

08:48.730 --> 08:49.931
it's not impossible.

08:51.331 --> 08:53.931
But your future wife

08:54.051 --> 08:55.770
must be easygoing.

08:56.130 --> 08:58.770
If she bullies me, I won't stand for it.

08:59.851 --> 09:02.051
Why are you only thinking
about being a concubine?

09:04.171 --> 09:06.730
What? Could it be

09:09.530 --> 09:11.451
that you'd marry me as your wife?

09:13.211 --> 09:14.051
Li Feibai,

09:14.291 --> 09:17.571
when I was little,
I already had a rough time.

09:18.211 --> 09:20.730
I can't let it happen again.

09:21.811 --> 09:24.291
I won't go anywhere except the capital.

09:24.410 --> 09:27.051
Apart from dancing,
I can't do any work at all.

09:27.851 --> 09:30.770
If you want me
to live a poor life with you,

09:30.931 --> 09:31.490
forget it.

09:33.770 --> 09:37.051
If you can't support me,
don't even think about marrying me.

09:39.130 --> 09:41.851
Well, that's not up to you.

09:45.051 --> 09:46.650
So smelly!

09:46.691 --> 09:47.650
Go wash up.

09:49.370 --> 09:50.410
Is it really that smelly?

09:50.410 --> 09:51.691
Yes, go!

09:54.608 --> 09:57.968
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

09:59.610 --> 10:03.091
Qin Cang,
under Marquis Muyang's command,

10:03.331 --> 10:06.331
committed serious crimes
and should be executed by law.

10:06.691 --> 10:09.331
However, you timely repented.

10:09.410 --> 10:11.931
You testified against your accomplices,

10:11.971 --> 10:13.370
truthfully confessed,

10:13.530 --> 10:17.171
and voluntarily presented the evidence
of Marquis Muyang's crimes.

10:17.291 --> 10:19.171
That was quite helpful.

10:19.451 --> 10:21.851
Therefore, you're treated
with exceptional leniency.

10:22.010 --> 10:25.010
By special grace, your life is spared.

10:25.171 --> 10:27.331
Your property is to be confiscated,

10:27.490 --> 10:29.171
and you are exiled to Qianchuan.

10:30.610 --> 10:33.770
Yes, I appreciate it.

10:59.171 --> 11:02.490
The Empress Dowager asks
if you have anything else to say.

11:03.530 --> 11:06.770
Since she has already treated me
as a discarded pawn,

11:08.530 --> 11:10.530
I have nothing more to say.

11:12.890 --> 11:14.130
I only ask for one thing.

11:15.091 --> 11:17.291
I hope Tianyang will be safe and sound.

11:20.650 --> 11:21.890
After all these years,

11:23.291 --> 11:25.490
I have not failed the Empress Dowager.

11:32.610 --> 11:33.410
Keep up.

11:44.691 --> 11:47.971
Qin Cang, you're not dead!

11:53.130 --> 11:54.451
Sorry to disappoint you.

11:55.691 --> 11:58.370
I'm lucky to be alive.

12:00.171 --> 12:01.171
Marquis Muyang,

12:01.971 --> 12:05.010
Qin Cang has confessed
that Chen Longxiang is still alive,

12:05.051 --> 12:07.171
and that Gongshu Yang

12:07.171 --> 12:10.931
found out the concrete evidence

12:10.931 --> 12:12.610
of the weaponry case.

12:57.650 --> 12:59.010
I never thought

12:59.931 --> 13:02.370
I would be defeated by my own hand.

13:10.851 --> 13:14.610
May I have a few final words
with Marquis Muyang?

13:19.490 --> 13:22.610
Well, I'll let you two talk.

13:38.211 --> 13:41.010
When I was a kid,
I lived with my mom alone.

13:42.171 --> 13:45.010
At 14, you brought me back
to your house.

13:45.770 --> 13:48.211
You hired a coach
to teach me martial arts.

13:49.171 --> 13:50.650
The old servants told me

13:52.370 --> 13:54.096
I was also a young master in the house,

13:55.650 --> 13:56.851
and your son.

14:04.130 --> 14:05.211
But you never

14:07.451 --> 14:09.331
treated me as your son.

14:19.171 --> 14:20.451
You sent me to Cangbei

14:21.410 --> 14:23.010
to smuggle weapons out of the pass.

14:25.171 --> 14:26.730
You made me kill for you

14:27.171 --> 14:28.610
to eliminate your adversaries.

14:29.451 --> 14:32.010
You asked me to amass wealth
and collude with the enemy.

14:32.490 --> 14:34.451
You made me do all sorts of dirty deeds.

14:38.571 --> 14:40.370
It was because I valued you.

14:41.331 --> 14:42.250
Did you?

14:46.571 --> 14:48.010
Then why did you want to kill me?

15:02.370 --> 15:03.010
Marquis Muyang,

15:06.971 --> 15:08.451
I just want to ask you one thing.

15:13.130 --> 15:14.171
Without me,

15:15.530 --> 15:18.571
if it were Zhou Tianyang instead,
what would you have done?

15:22.800 --> 15:26.610
Would you also have silenced him
for your own protection?

15:36.410 --> 15:39.610
Although you never treated me as a son,

15:41.370 --> 15:42.530
in my heart,

15:45.776 --> 15:47.376
you will always be my father.

16:05.971 --> 16:08.250
Marquis Muyang, you gave me life.

16:09.010 --> 16:11.490
For all these years, you have raised me

16:12.650 --> 16:13.451
and taught me.

16:16.691 --> 16:18.931
I'm grateful to you.

17:02.650 --> 17:03.451
Father.

17:09.130 --> 17:09.930
Take care.

18:03.690 --> 18:04.610
They're here.

18:06.128 --> 18:07.210
Come on.

18:10.450 --> 18:11.251
What are you doing?

18:12.610 --> 18:14.331
We are the family of Young Master Qin.

18:14.610 --> 18:15.851
It will be a long journey.

18:16.291 --> 18:17.851
Thank you for escorting him.

18:21.930 --> 18:25.210
That's okay.
We'll take good care of him on the road.

18:26.731 --> 18:27.930
We've prepared some food.

18:28.210 --> 18:29.610
Please have some before you go.

18:31.731 --> 18:32.531
Alright.

18:33.011 --> 18:34.491
Be quick. We're kind of in a rush.

18:41.690 --> 18:44.491
Master, I got you some money and stuff.

18:44.771 --> 18:45.851
Take it with you.

18:46.890 --> 18:47.811
Where is Zhou Tianyang?

18:49.690 --> 18:51.370
He is at home.

18:53.091 --> 18:54.251
Tell him from me

18:54.811 --> 18:56.491
he should give up.

18:56.650 --> 18:58.170
He should leave the capital right now

18:58.170 --> 19:00.130
to go to his mother in Lingnan.

19:00.170 --> 19:02.571
Yes, I will certainly tell him.

19:03.331 --> 19:06.370
Master, the journey to Qianchuan
is long and tough.

19:07.210 --> 19:08.130
Take care.

19:13.970 --> 19:14.771
Thank you.

19:22.731 --> 19:24.650
Master, give it to us.

19:35.091 --> 19:36.291
My room is over there.

19:38.650 --> 19:41.210
Your mansion looks nothing special.

19:47.771 --> 19:49.531
There is not even a decent plaque.

19:50.192 --> 19:52.784
(Tuisi Pavilion)

19:53.130 --> 19:55.610
Isn't your Lishan Academy quite famous?

19:56.091 --> 19:59.450
At your wedding, your tutors
didn't even give you an inscription?

20:12.771 --> 20:15.051
This little fish is even shorter
than my nail protector.

20:18.811 --> 20:20.210
What is this place used for?

20:24.011 --> 20:25.811
So, you can actually fish here?

20:26.571 --> 20:28.130
That's quite a nice hobby.

20:31.210 --> 20:34.170
Ye Ying, why exactly did you come?

20:48.811 --> 20:49.370
Bring tea.

20:50.091 --> 20:50.690
Yes.

20:52.970 --> 20:54.731
Your Highness, I'll go help.

21:01.970 --> 21:03.331
Ye Li,

21:03.331 --> 21:06.091
there's something
I don't know who to ask.

21:06.531 --> 21:09.771
After thinking it over,
I want to hear your opinion.

21:10.930 --> 21:14.370
You actually want my opinion
on something? That's rare.

21:15.450 --> 21:18.011
Don't interrupt. I'm serious.

21:19.410 --> 21:20.011
Go ahead.

21:23.011 --> 21:25.051
His Highness passed away so suddenly,

21:25.051 --> 21:26.610
and didn't have any children.

21:28.091 --> 21:30.210
He was the only bloodline
of the former crown prince.

21:30.731 --> 21:33.690
His death cuts off the bloodline.

21:34.051 --> 21:36.336
Recently, some people around me
have advised me

21:36.450 --> 21:39.650
to adopt a clever child

21:39.650 --> 21:41.771
from close relatives.

21:42.771 --> 21:45.130
Then, His Highness will have a child

21:45.130 --> 21:47.051
to inherit his heritage.

21:47.851 --> 21:49.771
What's your take on this?

21:53.091 --> 21:55.571
Say something! What do you think?

22:03.091 --> 22:06.410
Ye Ying, you are still young.

22:06.970 --> 22:09.091
Why tie down your entire life so early?

22:09.771 --> 22:11.210
If you live in an empty house

22:11.531 --> 22:14.410
and raise a child who is not your own,

22:15.690 --> 22:16.970
is it worth it?

22:19.370 --> 22:22.890
His Highness is dead,
but I have to move on.

22:23.331 --> 22:24.811
Sure, you do.

22:25.610 --> 22:28.450
But to move on,
you have more than one choice.

22:42.251 --> 22:44.210
Nowadays, social customs are more open.

22:44.571 --> 22:46.851
A woman can divorce her husband,

22:47.051 --> 22:48.531
can take the imperial examinations,

22:49.811 --> 22:51.491
can engage in business,

22:51.491 --> 22:52.930
can study and write books,

22:52.930 --> 22:55.251
and even become an official.

22:55.771 --> 22:57.771
Take Lady Lin, who writes books,

22:57.771 --> 23:00.851
and Mrs. Yu,
the wealthy silkworm raiser.

23:00.851 --> 23:02.731
Both of them are living a splendid life.

23:03.811 --> 23:05.450
Besides, you also know

23:05.450 --> 23:07.410
Mo Jingli is the son
of the former crown prince.

23:07.771 --> 23:10.450
His identity is already a shackle.

23:10.450 --> 23:11.571
All these years,

23:11.571 --> 23:14.571
the Empress Dowager and His Majesty
have been deeply wary of him.

23:14.571 --> 23:16.890
If you adopt a child now,

23:16.890 --> 23:19.851
from the moment
that child enters Prince Li's Mansion,

23:19.851 --> 23:22.051
he will also bear the shackle.

23:22.531 --> 23:24.690
He cannot be an official
to pursue his ambitions,

23:24.690 --> 23:26.491
and must live on thin ice,

23:27.170 --> 23:30.170
and may even become someone else's pawn,

23:30.491 --> 23:32.690
enticed and exploited,

23:33.370 --> 23:36.210
ultimately drawn into a vortex,
just like Mo Jingli.

23:36.930 --> 23:38.331
You won't be able to protect him.

23:43.610 --> 23:44.851
Think twice.

23:45.731 --> 23:49.331
You have a long way to go,
and don't rush to decide.

23:53.731 --> 23:55.690
You always have a lot to say.

23:57.130 --> 23:59.130
But does what I said make sense?

24:22.170 --> 24:24.650
Master Qin, have some?

24:28.210 --> 24:29.011
Thank you.

24:35.771 --> 24:38.091
That carriage behind
has been following us for a while.

24:40.130 --> 24:42.251
It looks like a rich family's carriage.

24:43.210 --> 24:44.571
But still, stay alert.

24:44.571 --> 24:45.650
Just in case.

25:41.811 --> 25:43.410
Come on, guys, try some.

25:43.410 --> 25:44.450
It's our own meat.

25:46.011 --> 25:48.771
When traveling, we should look out
for each other. Try it.

25:49.170 --> 25:50.011
- Come on.
- Alright.

25:50.011 --> 25:51.811
Well, thank you then.

25:55.130 --> 25:57.210
Where are you heading?

25:57.370 --> 25:58.930
We are going to Qianchuan.

25:58.930 --> 26:01.210
Qianchuan? What a coincidence!

26:01.210 --> 26:02.811
We are also going to Qianchuan.

26:03.051 --> 26:04.210
What a coincidence!

26:04.210 --> 26:05.731
Sit. Enjoy your food.

26:05.731 --> 26:07.531
- Let me know if you need more.
- Alright, thanks.

28:20.210 --> 28:21.410
(I am Lin Tinglan.)

28:21.811 --> 28:24.130
(T I N G, L A N.)

28:26.610 --> 28:27.370
Have a try.

28:30.930 --> 28:33.571
(Turns out a melon cut with your knife
tastes this sweet.)

28:34.370 --> 28:35.610
(I told you it was sweet.)

28:35.888 --> 28:38.576
(Lakeview Garden)

28:45.011 --> 28:46.051
Master Qin, you're awake.

28:48.170 --> 28:49.650
Come on, we're hitting the road soon.

28:50.130 --> 28:52.610
And you have to put this on.

28:55.450 --> 28:56.011
Alright.

29:03.280 --> 29:05.200
(Lakeview Garden)

29:10.650 --> 29:13.851
My Lady, why don't we go with them?

29:14.210 --> 29:15.771
We can look out for him on the road.

29:15.851 --> 29:18.731
And Young Master Qin
will suffer a bit less.

29:21.170 --> 29:24.610
He broke the law. He deserves this.

29:24.771 --> 29:27.091
Are we still going to Qianchuan?

29:28.731 --> 29:29.531
Yes.

29:30.571 --> 29:33.851
Qianchuan is a beautiful place.
Of course, we are going there.

29:35.331 --> 29:36.531
As for him and me,

29:38.011 --> 29:41.531
if we're meant to meet again, we will.

29:44.170 --> 29:44.970
Let's go.

29:49.531 --> 29:51.370
Make way.

29:52.930 --> 29:53.811
Sir.

29:54.811 --> 29:56.130
Make way.

29:59.130 --> 30:01.970
After countless hardships,

30:01.970 --> 30:05.170
Liu Sanlang finally married Lady Meng.

30:05.491 --> 30:06.930
Unexpectedly,

30:06.930 --> 30:09.970
Liu Sanlang's mother
didn't like Lady Meng.

30:10.370 --> 30:13.450
One moment, she scolded Lady Meng
for being impolite,

30:13.970 --> 30:17.650
and the next, she blamed Lady Meng
for being unable to do farm work.

30:17.771 --> 30:20.368
She found fault with everything

30:20.368 --> 30:24.291
and cruelly broke a lovely couple up.

30:24.771 --> 30:29.690
With a letter of divorce,
Lady Meng was kicked out of their home.

30:30.291 --> 30:32.091
By the Willow Pavilion,

30:32.450 --> 30:35.450
Liu Sanlang led his horse
to see her off.

30:35.690 --> 30:37.531
They walked side by side.

30:37.531 --> 30:40.331
When they reached the fork in the road,
they burst into tears.

30:41.410 --> 30:42.650
Liu Sanlang said,

30:44.251 --> 30:45.051
"My dear,

30:45.531 --> 30:48.930
today you go home for now,

30:49.011 --> 30:50.811
but I will surely bring you back soon.

30:51.331 --> 30:53.251
Once I have pacified my mother,

30:53.251 --> 30:56.752
I will personally go find you
and bring you home."

30:57.370 --> 31:00.331
Lady Meng looked at her husband,

31:00.450 --> 31:02.650
tears sparkling in her eyes.

31:02.970 --> 31:04.251
Forcing a smile, she said,

31:04.450 --> 31:07.771
"I hope you'll remember what you said.

31:07.890 --> 31:09.552
No matter what happens,

31:09.552 --> 31:11.890
do not betray me."

31:12.011 --> 31:14.832
They swore to heaven

31:14.832 --> 31:18.051
and parted in tears.

31:21.930 --> 31:24.176
To know what happens next,

31:24.176 --> 31:27.376
come and listen again.

31:27.930 --> 31:29.610
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

31:29.851 --> 31:30.650
Good story!

31:31.011 --> 31:31.851
Bravo!

31:33.170 --> 31:33.690
Thank you.

31:33.690 --> 31:36.144
Make way.

31:36.144 --> 31:37.051
Thank you.

31:37.051 --> 31:39.248
Make way.

31:39.248 --> 31:40.011
Thank you.

31:47.251 --> 31:49.251
You've been coming here often
these days,

31:49.450 --> 31:50.731
just to listen to this?

31:52.410 --> 31:55.450
I haven't heard this story before.
It must be a new story.

31:57.450 --> 31:58.251
So,

31:58.811 --> 32:02.410
can Lady Meng and Liu Sanlang
end up together?

32:04.130 --> 32:05.210
Probably not.

32:06.650 --> 32:07.450
Why not?

32:09.571 --> 32:11.610
Liu Sanlang's father died
in corvée labor,

32:11.771 --> 32:14.531
and Lady Meng's elder brother
was the overseer at the time.

32:15.370 --> 32:17.771
That's why Liu Sanlang's mother

32:18.091 --> 32:19.331
doesn't like Lady Meng

32:19.531 --> 32:20.690
and constantly nitpicks her.

32:21.531 --> 32:23.930
And Liu Sanlang is a filial son,

32:24.051 --> 32:26.130
unable to defy his mother.

32:26.851 --> 32:27.890
So, it's quite tricky.

32:30.491 --> 32:33.291
Maybe Lady Meng can move Mrs. Liu.

32:33.776 --> 32:36.650
After all, she has nothing to do
with the death of Mrs. Liu's husband.

32:36.650 --> 32:37.851
She is not to blame.

32:40.370 --> 32:41.370
If you like,

32:41.690 --> 32:43.930
we can pay off the storyteller

32:43.930 --> 32:45.970
and make him tell the story
the way you want.

32:53.130 --> 32:55.251
Where is Feng Zhiyao? Where did he go?

32:59.851 --> 33:02.130
He's been in a bad mood lately
and left the capital

33:02.450 --> 33:04.051
to clear his mind.

33:10.011 --> 33:13.331
Li, I want
to discuss something with you.

33:14.771 --> 33:15.571
What is it?

33:17.130 --> 33:20.291
Look, Marquis Muyang has fallen,

33:20.571 --> 33:23.251
and my clan's name has been cleared.

33:24.130 --> 33:25.731
It's all over now.

33:26.930 --> 33:30.130
You are not Lady Meng,
and I am not Liu Sanlang.

33:30.731 --> 33:34.170
From now on,
the two of us can be together happily.

33:35.170 --> 33:36.650
You will never be alone again.

33:40.531 --> 33:44.531
So, can you let Qingshuang
go back to her own home?

33:47.130 --> 33:47.930
Why?

33:51.571 --> 33:54.531
Now, there are plenty of servants
in our mansion,

33:55.210 --> 33:57.130
and Qingyu has been serving you.

33:57.890 --> 33:59.491
Just let Qingshuang go home, okay?

34:00.610 --> 34:04.251
She's stayed with you for eight years.
It's time for her to go home.

34:07.130 --> 34:08.970
But Qingshuang has always been with me.

34:10.530 --> 34:13.651
I will always be with you, alright?

34:20.771 --> 34:21.570
Alright.

34:24.771 --> 34:25.890
You agreed?

34:27.331 --> 34:29.090
I'll tell Qingshuang about it later.

34:29.570 --> 34:30.930
And don't think about her anymore.

34:31.450 --> 34:34.530
From now on, whatever is on your mind,

34:35.291 --> 34:38.731
or whatever you want to say,
just tell me.

34:39.570 --> 34:40.370
Alright?

34:42.090 --> 34:44.624
Alright, but never get tired of me.

34:48.784 --> 34:52.208
(Now the enemy frequently nosed around.)

35:05.370 --> 35:09.171
Zhou Jing, you are authoritarian,
forming cliques for personal gain.

35:09.171 --> 35:11.570
You framed loyal officials,
causing wrongful convictions.

35:11.611 --> 35:13.771
You smuggled weapons
and betrayed the nation.

35:14.010 --> 35:17.450
With all these charges,
which one is unjust to you?

35:17.811 --> 35:19.731
Even if you refuse to plead guilty,

35:20.131 --> 35:22.010
I can still convict you.

35:28.811 --> 35:31.851
Marquis Muyang, you should understand.

35:32.331 --> 35:36.050
At this point,
denying what you did is futile.

35:36.890 --> 35:39.570
Do you have any last wishes?

35:40.731 --> 35:41.851
I want to see Mo Xiuyao.

35:43.970 --> 35:46.010
Prince Ding is not
in charge of this case.

35:46.291 --> 35:47.651
What's the point of seeing him?

35:48.291 --> 35:50.010
Even if he is supervising the case,

35:50.611 --> 35:52.370
given what you've done to his clan,

35:52.370 --> 35:53.691
do you think he will let you off?

35:56.490 --> 35:57.611
As long as I see him,

35:58.410 --> 36:00.811
this case will be concluded.

36:04.848 --> 36:06.512
(Qingfeng Mingyue Tower)

36:08.970 --> 36:11.450
Your Highnesses, it just rained.

36:11.450 --> 36:13.291
Our carriage is stuck
at the intersection.

36:13.331 --> 36:14.890
They'll be here in a moment.

36:18.691 --> 36:19.490
Yao.

36:22.090 --> 36:24.291
Liu Sanlang and Lady Meng

36:24.731 --> 36:26.691
really can't be together forever?

36:27.771 --> 36:30.771
Why are you still thinking about it?
It's just a story.

36:31.370 --> 36:32.450
Answer me.

36:35.291 --> 36:36.131
I don't know.

36:36.691 --> 36:38.970
Things change, and people change.

36:39.811 --> 36:42.291
People's thinking is variable

36:42.490 --> 36:43.570
and uncertain.

36:44.131 --> 36:46.171
A thought arises.
And then, a thought disappears.

36:48.530 --> 36:49.490
How they choose

36:50.890 --> 36:53.851
is up to them, not us.

36:56.930 --> 36:59.490
Then let's come back in a few days
and listen to the ending.

37:00.291 --> 37:00.851
Alright.

37:06.450 --> 37:07.970
Your Highnesses.

37:08.611 --> 37:09.851
Chen Longxiang has confessed.

37:09.968 --> 37:12.450
Gongshu Yang and Murong Shen
are interrogating Marquis Muyang.

37:12.450 --> 37:15.251
But Marquis Muyang
suddenly wanted to see you.

37:15.570 --> 37:17.131
Gongshu Yang wants you there right now.

37:20.291 --> 37:22.050
I'll go there, and you go home.

37:42.811 --> 37:43.611
Go.

37:48.944 --> 37:53.104
♪You always love with pain♪

37:54.576 --> 38:00.208
♪Forgetting you deserve to be loved too♪

38:02.768 --> 38:08.272
♪How the rain outside
nurtures the heart♪

38:09.072 --> 38:13.456
♪That's how you are cherished♪

38:14.704 --> 38:18.064
♪You don't need to chase♪

38:18.064 --> 38:21.584
♪After clouds that winds pursue♪

38:21.584 --> 38:24.688
♪You can silently watch each sunrise♪

38:25.072 --> 38:28.112
♪Finding happiness by your side♪

38:28.400 --> 38:31.696
♪You don't need to chart a map♪

38:31.696 --> 38:35.152
♪Of every bend where love winds on♪

38:35.504 --> 38:38.672
♪Nor travel far to guide its course♪

38:38.672 --> 38:40.496
♪To make your heart♪

38:40.880 --> 38:44.080
♪Warm again♪

38:59.171 --> 38:59.970
Stop!

39:01.251 --> 39:02.171
- Your Highness.
- What's wrong?

39:02.171 --> 39:03.312
Her Highness is behind us.

39:07.691 --> 39:08.651
Why did you come?

39:10.331 --> 39:11.450
Did I run fast?

39:13.570 --> 39:14.370
What's wrong?

39:15.211 --> 39:16.450
Let's come back tomorrow.

39:17.691 --> 39:18.410
What?

39:18.410 --> 39:19.410
To listen to the story.

39:19.691 --> 39:22.651
To hear the story of Liu Sanlang
and Lady Meng. Come again tomorrow.

39:23.664 --> 39:26.864
♪You don't need to chase♪

39:28.930 --> 39:31.530
Alright, as you wish.

39:35.890 --> 39:37.552
Don't get wet, or you may catch a cold.

39:38.090 --> 39:39.010
Go home.

39:41.890 --> 39:42.691
See you at home.

39:44.112 --> 39:47.472
♪Nor travel far to guide its course♪

39:47.696 --> 39:49.264
♪To make your heart♪

39:49.776 --> 39:52.976
♪Warm again♪

39:55.120 --> 39:58.480
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

40:05.970 --> 40:06.811
Prince Ding.

40:08.090 --> 40:10.171
Marquis Muyang
is insisting on seeing you.

40:15.331 --> 40:17.171
We'll leave it to you now.

40:17.490 --> 40:18.331
Sure.

40:26.890 --> 40:27.691
You want to see me?

40:40.331 --> 40:42.490
Prince Ding, you look good.

40:43.211 --> 40:44.970
You must have been happy lately.

40:47.010 --> 40:49.090
Seeing your current situation,

40:49.490 --> 40:52.211
I can't help feeling happy.

40:56.410 --> 40:57.811
It's risky to be an official.

40:58.771 --> 41:00.410
Today, you're flattered by all.

41:01.010 --> 41:03.010
Tomorrow, you're a prisoner.

41:03.811 --> 41:05.930
Too early for you to celebrate.

41:07.090 --> 41:08.010
Eight years ago,

41:09.410 --> 41:13.090
you were in this cell,
while I was outside the cell.

41:14.970 --> 41:17.410
Yes. What a pity.

41:18.530 --> 41:21.811
Now, you're in this cell,
while I'm outside.

41:27.930 --> 41:30.530
Things are ever-changing

41:31.131 --> 41:32.530
and unpredictable.

41:33.771 --> 41:37.291
The rise and fall of a person happens,
as illusory as a dream.

41:38.010 --> 41:40.811
Back then, when I was in Huaixi,

41:42.331 --> 41:45.131
I lived in a room of this size,

41:47.930 --> 41:50.010
a side room made of straw mats.

41:51.851 --> 41:52.851
Every time it rained,

41:54.010 --> 41:57.131
the floor was all damp,
and I almost couldn't move.

41:58.291 --> 42:01.890
Later, I was recommended
to take the prefectural exam.

42:02.570 --> 42:06.291
And because of my outstanding results,
I had the chance to become an official.

42:07.090 --> 42:09.851
And then, step by step,
I entered the central government

42:10.370 --> 42:13.090
and rose to my current position.

42:14.291 --> 42:15.568
But who would have thought

42:16.530 --> 42:17.970
that in the end, I would return

42:18.811 --> 42:21.171
to a dark, small room before death.

42:21.731 --> 42:25.251
If you want to express your feelings,
you've found the wrong person.

42:27.490 --> 42:28.811
The imperial family is heartless.

42:30.010 --> 42:32.890
The court has been rotten,

42:32.890 --> 42:34.651
full of hypocritical beasts.

42:36.811 --> 42:38.611
But you are one of those

42:39.651 --> 42:42.251
I think much of.

42:43.984 --> 42:46.640
(Preview)

42:46.811 --> 42:49.171
Aren't you curious

42:49.651 --> 42:53.171
who cheated your brother
out of the late Emperor's edict?

42:53.211 --> 42:53.970
Shut up!

42:54.410 --> 42:55.851
Just wait to die!

42:56.211 --> 43:00.050
Was it your mom who cheated my brother
out of the late Emperor's edict?

43:00.490 --> 43:01.050
Yes.

43:01.771 --> 43:02.450
Your Highness!

43:03.530 --> 43:04.331
Yao...

43:05.010 --> 43:06.131
He's dead.

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
♪Unbound by form♪
